首先我们准备适量的小青椒和小米辣去蒂备用
First, prepare a moderate amount of "xiaoqingjiao" and "xiaomila" chili peppers, remove the stems and set aside

此辣椒碧绿短小辣度适中
This pepper appears to be jade green, short and medium spicy

是由湖南本土优质辣椒种子而结果
They're fruits of premium Hunan local pepper seeds

怕辣的同学可以选择辣度较低的大青椒
You may replace it with the less spicy  "Daqingjiao" (Green Bell Peper)

然后将辣椒清洗干净捞出备用
Wash the peppers throughly, drain the water, then set aside

下一步开始准备辅料
Next, Prepare prepare the "Fu Liao" ("auxiliary ingredients")

准备五花肉1小块切成厚片之后剁碎备用
Cut a small chunk of pork belly into thick slices, then mince it and set aside

加半肥瘦的五花肉爆香之后成菜会更有层次感
Stir fry the half-fat pork belly till aromatic, so as to enrich the sense of layers of the product

准备大蒜几颗拍散之后剁碎备用
Crush and mince a few gloves of garlics, and set aside
            
同学们大蒜是虎皮青椒的灵魂所以一定不能少
Note that garlic is irreplaceable as it serves as the soul of "Hupi Qingjiao"(Tiger Skin Green Pepper)

下一步开始制作
Next, start cooking

首先我们把锅烧热
First, heat the wok

锅烧热之后将辣椒下锅
After the wok heats up, put in the peppers

然后烧小火将辣椒挤压翻炒6分钟左右
Then stir fry on low heat for 6 minutes, and pewaa the peppers while frying

这一步的目的是将辣椒的表皮通过高温炒糊炒香
This step serves to caramalize and aromatize the skin of the peppers through high temp.

同学们切记这一步不能放油
Remember to NEVER add oil during the process

之后经过慢火挤压翻炒的辣椒才够香辣
Also note that only after the low-heat "Squeeze-Fry" procedure shall the peppers turn fragrant and spicy

当辣椒炒至表面焦香后取出备用
Take out the peppers once the skin turns brown and fragrant, and set aside

下一步开始炒肉末
Next step, move to cook the ground meat

锅烧热之后加入适量的菜籽油下锅
Add moderate amount of rapeseed oil after the wok heats up

油温6成热之后将剁好的肉末下锅翻炒至干香
When the oil is 60% done, add minced meat and stir fry till dried&aromatic

当肉末炒至干香后加入蒜蓉翻炒均匀
Then add the minced garlics, stir fry evenly

然后再加入干香的辣椒下锅
Add the cooked peppers

下一步开始调味
Next, season the dish

锅中加入适量的酱油从锅边淋入翻炒几下
Add a moderate amount of soy sauce from the edge of the wok, and stir fry

当炒出锅汽之后再加入适量的食用盐
Add some salt after "Guo Qi"(wok hei) emerges

同学们食用盐可以略微多一点点这样才够味
You may add a liitle bit more salt to enhance the favor

再加入小半勺白糖翻炒均匀即可出锅装盘
Add half a spoon of sugar and stir fry evenly. The dish is ready to serve

一道香辣下饭的家常虎皮青椒就制作完成
We have finished cooking a delicious home dish "Hupi Qingjiao"(Tiger Skin Green Pepper) 

下面开始技术总结
第一，不同辣椒的种类辣度也不一样，大家可以选择适合自己的辣椒
第二，辣椒下锅必须小火慢炒，炒至辣椒表皮脱层干香即可
第三，此菜可以不加肉末，但蒜蓉是必不可少
Technical Summary:
1: Chilli peppers vary in the degree of spiciness, you may choose according to your preference
2: Chilli peppers must be cooked on low heat, fry untill the outter layer detached, dried and aromatic
3: While ground meat counts as optional, garlics are a must to the dish

下面开始试吃
Next we'll try the dish~~

经过一番制作我们这个辣椒已经做好了
We've done making the chili peppers

但是它辣不辣我们还不知道 要吃了才知道
We are not sure weather it's spicy, gotta try it first

辣度中等偏下
Medium-low spicy...

因为我们比较能吃辣所有这个菜我没放醋
We are used to spiciness so I did not add vineger 

如果你不能吃辣的话可以放点醋
You can add some if this is too spicy for you

加点醋进去稀释一下它这个辣度
Adding some vinegar can dilute the spiciness

这个吃起来非常下饭
This dish is good to eat with rice

很适合这样子对于白米饭
Especially for white rice

如果是干吃的话
If you just eat the dish without any company

会非常恼火
It's gonna be bad

我们做这种辣椒的时候
While cooking the peppers

最需要注意的是这个辣椒
It is important that the pepper...

下完锅后一定要干炒把它吵到软
...must be fried without oil till softened

炒到干香
...dried & aromatic

然后再放肉进去炒
Then you can add meat for stir frying

我们一般在饭店里做这个辣椒
Usually in restaurant 

基本上是宽油伺候
we cook this dish with "broad oil"

为什么呢，节省时间
Why? To save time!

这个肉末非常香
The meat is very fragrant

喜欢吃肉末可以多加些
You can add more if you are into minced meat

其实这个是简配版的
This is actually a simplified version

高端版可以加点豆shi
For improved version you can add fermented bean

放牛肉粒
and beef dices

又香又辣
both aromatic and spicy

这个辣椒很适合这种土灶来炒
It's good to cook this kind of pepper on a firewood stove

就是用柴火慢慢的把这个辣椒煸香
Use firewood to slowly stir-fry the pepper till aromatic

非常下饭大家可以回去试一下
Good company with rice, everybody can try in your house

